				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$dB/dt$\end{document} which is crucial for space weather forecasting in the magnetosphere (discussed in more detail below) (Pulkkinen et al. 2013).

